#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&knetattach; is a wizard which makes it easier to integrate your network "
"resources with your &kde; Desktop."
msgstr ""
"&knetattach; es un asistente que le ayuda a integrar los recursos de red en "
"su escritorio &kde;."

#. Tag: keyword
